    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed at MRL 2. Uncertainty quantification via Monte Carlo confirms RH < 1.0 at 95th percentile across the CPB operating envelope. The UQ analysis incorporated a screening sensitivity study identifying dominant input contributors to NIH variability; these findings are documented in the UQ narrative and support confidence in the model predictions. Overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory decision for this Class II CPB device.",
